OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780168284
OL,3,CCannibal killer refused parole for
OL,4,Cninth time
OL,6,FA killer who boasted that he had eaten
OL,7,Fparts of his victim with a plate of
OL,8,Fpasta has had parole refused for a
OL,9,Fninth time.
OL,11,FDavid Harker, now 51, killed mother-of-
OL,12,Ffour Julie Paterson, 32, in Darlington
OL,13,Fin 1998 and only some of her remains
OL,14,Fhave ever been found.
OL,16,FHe is serving a life sentence after
OL,17,Fadmitting manslaughter on the grounds
OL,18,Fof diminished responsibility.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
