FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780168284
OL,3,CCannibal killer refused parole for
OL,4,Cninth time
OL,6,FPrevious decisions have been made
OL,7,Fusing documents but the latest, ninth,
OL,8,Fheard oral evidence. Harker did not
OL,9,Fattend or make representations.
OL,11,FThe panel considered a dossier
OL,12,Fcontaining 356 pages of reports,
OL,13,Fincluding submissions on behalf of the
OL,14,FSecretary of State arguing against
OL,15,Frelease.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
