OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780168284
OL,3,CCannibal killer refused parole for
OL,4,Cninth time
OL,6,FIt heard from the person responsible
OL,7,Ffor managing Harker in jail, two
OL,8,Fprobation officers who would be
OL,9,Fresponsible for managing him in the
OL,10,Fcommunity, a psychologist and someone
OL,11,Fwho worked with him on a programme in
OL,12,Fprison.
OL,14,FWhile the person who worked with him
OL,15,Fon the programme was not allowed to
OL,16,Frecommend a course of action, the
OL,17,Fothers said Harker did not pass the
OL,18,Ftest for release.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
