PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780168284
OL,3,CCannibal killer refused parole for
OL,4,Cninth time
OL,6,FIn its conclusion, a Parole Board
OL,7,Fsummary of the decision said: "The
OL,8,Fpanel carefully analysed all the
OL,9,Fevidence and formed its own
OL,10,Findependent assessment of risk.
OL,12,F"It decided not to direct the release
OL,13,Fof David Harker, nor to recommend to
OL,14,Fthe Secretary of State that David
OL,15,FHarker should be transferred to open
OL,16,Fconditions."
